203
00:12:00,679 --> 00:12:01,759
Okay, wait for me a moment.

204
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:02,559
I'll be right back.

205
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:13,559
Please sit.

206
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,559
