207
00:12:16,919 --> 00:12:19,120
The outside world has many prejudices against Cang Feng.

208
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,720
But today, everyone has seen

209
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:23,360
that Cang Feng members are not only law-abiding and polite,

210
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:25,919
but also very presentable.

211
00:12:27,799 --> 00:12:28,159
