215
00:12:48,399 --> 00:12:49,519
Thank you, thanks.

216
00:12:59,799 --> 00:13:01,879
Next, let's welcome the famous movie star

217
00:13:01,879 --> 00:13:04,279
and beauty pageant champion, Miss Zhu Shuyi,

218
00:13:04,279 --> 00:13:07,039
to give the opening speech and cut the ribbon.

219
00:13:07,919 --> 00:13:09,480
