264
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,679
Hao Yu, you witch!

265
00:15:28,279 --> 00:15:29,399
Isn't this mess big enough?

266
00:15:29,759 --> 00:15:30,480
Ji Zhijie.

267
00:15:30,879 --> 00:15:31,399
It was her.

268
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,000
It's all her doing.

269
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,279
She made Zhu Shuyi wear white shoes on purpose.

270
00:15:35,279 --> 00:15:36,200
To match that outfit of hers.

271
00:15:36,639 --> 00:15:38,200
I knew it. You're always so cunning.

272
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:40,320
