276
00:15:47,799 --> 00:15:49,039
You wanted Wei Hao to think...

277
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:50,360
...that Zhu Shuyi was you.

278
00:15:50,919 --> 00:15:51,919
You planned all of this.

279
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,120
You planned it.

280
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,600
