284
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:07,879
I even told you to pick shoes of a different color.

285
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,679
You were the ones who insisted on that color.

286
00:16:09,679 --> 00:16:11,000
Xiao Cui can testify for me.

287
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,039
Yes.

288
00:16:12,519 --> 00:16:13,399
Miss Hao said...

289
00:16:13,559 --> 00:16:15,519
...choosing gold would solve everything.

290
00:16:15,879 --> 00:16:17,120
But Sis Jiali said...

291
00:16:17,279 --> 00:16:19,200
...even if we strip Miss Hao's clothes off...

292
00:16:19,559 --> 00:16:20,559
...we have to choose white.

293
00:16:21,159 --> 00:16:22,600
Miss Hao had nothing to wear...

294
00:16:22,879 --> 00:16:23,759
...so she had to dress like this.

295
00:16:23,879 --> 00:16:24,639
Shut your mouth!

296
00:16:26,799 --> 00:16:28,519
Hao Yu, you're really good at setting traps.

297
00:16:29,519 --> 00:16:30,679
First, you pretended to obey me.

298
00:16:30,759 --> 00:16:32,080
You used reverse psychology to bait me.

299
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,120
Then you stole my keys...

300
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:35,639
...to go and let Wei Hao out.

301
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,399
You know Wei Hao hates you.

302
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:39,639
You deliberately wanted Wei Hao...

303
00:16:39,799 --> 00:16:41,399
...to make a fool of himself in public.

304
00:16:43,159 --> 00:16:43,759
Because...

305
00:16:44,279 --> 00:16:45,360
...you hate Wei Hao.

306
00:16:45,639 --> 00:16:48,320
You hate Wei Hao for killing your pig godfather.

307
00:16:50,440 --> 00:16:51,360
After I changed my clothes...

308
00:16:51,399 --> 00:16:53,279
...I was too afraid to see anyone.

309
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:56,600
Xiao Cui brought me a blanket.

310
00:16:57,399 --> 00:16:59,039
I was with her the whole time.

311
00:16:59,279 --> 00:17:01,039
How could I have let Wei Hao out?

312
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:03,159
How would I even know where Wei Hao was?

313
00:17:04,079 --> 00:17:04,880
Yes, that's right.

314
00:17:05,079 --> 00:17:05,880
I can testify.

315
00:17:06,279 --> 00:17:08,000
Miss Hao was waiting for me to get the clothes.

316
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:08,920
She didn't go anywhere.

317
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:09,680
She didn't do anything.

318
00:17:10,519 --> 00:17:12,880
It's just you two witches conspiring to trick me!

319
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:14,559
Fine.

320
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,759
Then you might as well say...

321
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:21,359
...that I gave Wei Hao the drugs he used...

322
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:23,559
...and that his screaming and violence up there...

323
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:25,680
...was because I possessed him too.

324
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:26,240
You...

325
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:28,640
I usually let it slide when you frame me.

326
00:17:29,759 --> 00:17:31,759
But today, the evidence and witnesses are all here.

327
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:35,599
I want Uncle Kun and Zhijie to judge this.

328
00:17:36,079 --> 00:17:38,039
Just because of my relationship with Guan Renjie...

329
00:17:38,119 --> 00:17:39,319
...you can't just frame me every time.

330
00:17:39,319 --> 00:17:40,640
I've really had enough.

331
00:17:45,559 --> 00:17:46,160
Zhijie.

332
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:49,519
Today...

333
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:52,319
...if I hadn't swapped clothes with Miss Zhu...

334
00:17:52,799 --> 00:17:53,880
...I can't even imagine...

335
00:17:54,759 --> 00:17:56,880
...if I had been the one on stage.

336
00:17:58,279 --> 00:18:00,119
I don't know what I did wrong.

337
00:18:01,599 --> 00:18:03,640
I don't know why they treat me like this.

338
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:05,400
I'll kill you!

339
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:15,359
Uncle Kun

340
00:18:19,559 --> 00:18:21,039
She's right.

341
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:23,599
If Wei Hao hadn't done wrong,

342
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:25,759
if Wei Hao

343
00:18:26,759 --> 00:18:29,440
hadn't caused a scene at such an important event,

344
00:18:31,400 --> 00:18:33,119
he wouldn't have given others an opportunity.

345
00:18:34,599 --> 00:18:35,640
I spent years

346
00:18:36,279 --> 00:18:37,839
building relationships with the councilors,

347
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:42,279
creating the image of the new Cang Feng.

348
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:46,319
You've ruined it all.

349
00:18:49,599 --> 00:18:50,319
Zhijie.

350
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:55,000
Drag Wei Hao to The Kennel.

351
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:56,640
Punish him by Gang Law.

352
00:18:56,799 --> 00:18:57,279
Don't!

353
00:18:57,799 --> 00:18:58,240
Uncle Kun!

354
00:18:58,720 --> 00:18:59,880
Uncle Kun, don't! Uncle Kun!

355
00:19:00,319 --> 00:19:00,880
The Kennel...

356
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:02,599
The torture at The Kennel is reserved for traitors!

357
00:19:03,079 --> 00:19:05,200
Wei Hao only made a mistake because he was framed!

358
00:19:06,839 --> 00:19:09,200
He can't withstand the torture at The Kennel!

359
00:19:10,839 --> 00:19:11,759
Uncle Kun!

360
00:19:12,480 --> 00:19:13,160
Zhijie.

361
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:17,119
The rest...

362
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:18,400
handle it yourself.

363
00:19:22,039 --> 00:19:22,599
Uncle Kun!

364
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:23,960
Uncle Kun!

365
00:19:34,279 --> 00:19:35,599
Uncle Kun!

366
00:19:39,519 --> 00:19:40,440
Uncle Kun!

367
00:19:40,759 --> 00:19:42,039
I'll see if Ji Zhijie

368
00:19:42,039 --> 00:19:43,880
will still want a slut like you then.

369
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:46,279
He's already like this.

370
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:48,079
Looks like his old habit kicked in again.

371
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:55,160
Wei Hao, you...

372
00:19:56,079 --> 00:19:57,319
Don't let me run into you again, Wei Hao.

373
00:19:57,480 --> 00:19:57,920
Let's go.

374
00:20:04,799 --> 00:20:05,880
I beg you.

375
00:20:06,599 --> 00:20:08,240
Just give me a little.

376
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:09,480
Give it to me.

377
00:20:12,359 --> 00:20:14,039
Just as I expected.

378
00:20:42,079 --> 00:20:43,000
Zhu Shuyi

379
00:20:44,119 --> 00:20:45,920
doesn't like gold this year.

380
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:47,640
I'll do it.

381
00:20:56,079 --> 00:20:58,640
I'll change Miss Zhu's shoes.

382
00:20:59,440 --> 00:21:00,160
Gold...

383
00:21:01,119 --> 00:21:03,079
Gold matches your outfit better.

384
00:21:04,319 --> 00:21:05,240
Gold is bad luck for me this year.

385
00:21:05,359 --> 00:21:06,000
You did it on purpose.

386
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,599
Isn't it simple?

387
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:09,480
You said it yourself,

388
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:11,279
white suits your outfit best.

389
00:21:11,759 --> 00:21:13,559
Just take off the dress and give it to Miss Zhu.

390
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:14,680
Wouldn't that solve it?

391
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:18,559
Uncle Kun is announcing today

392
00:21:18,759 --> 00:21:20,079
the manager of the nightclub.

393
00:21:26,039 --> 00:21:27,039
If I were you,

394
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,200
I'd be worried.

395
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:36,839
Xiao Cui.

396
00:21:37,119 --> 00:21:38,640
The ribbon-cutting has already started out front.

397
00:21:39,079 --> 00:21:40,119
Dressed like this,

398
00:21:40,279 --> 00:21:41,720
I really can't be seen by anyone.

399
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,920
Go to the front desk and find me a blanket.

400
00:21:45,079 --> 00:21:46,200
Let me cover up at least, right?

401
00:21:46,559 --> 00:21:47,599
Okay, wait a moment.

402
00:21:47,759 --> 00:21:48,480
I'll be right back.

403
00:23:02,319 --> 00:23:02,839
This...

404
00:23:03,519 --> 00:23:04,200
What?

405
00:23:15,359 --> 00:23:16,799
Miss Hao, here's the blanket.

406
00:23:18,279 --> 00:23:19,960
Can you help me take off the mask?

407
00:23:20,079 --> 00:23:20,559
Sure.

408
00:23:28,759 --> 00:23:29,200
Here.

409
00:23:29,759 --> 00:23:30,279
Thank you.

410
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:32,680
Let's go.

411
00:23:32,839 --> 00:23:33,279
Go.

412
00:24:17,599 --> 00:24:19,839
I'll strangle you! I'll strangle you!

413
00:24:22,359 --> 00:24:23,680
I want you dead!

414
00:24:24,119 --> 00:24:24,880
I'll kill you!

415
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:26,480
I'll strangle you!

416
00:24:27,559 --> 00:24:28,960
You slut!

417
00:24:34,119 --> 00:24:35,920
I'll kill you today, Hao Yu!

418
00:24:36,359 --> 00:24:37,240
You slut!

419
00:24:48,839 --> 00:24:50,640
Let Wei Hao go!

420
00:24:53,559 --> 00:24:54,400
Wei Hao!

421
00:25:00,279 --> 00:25:01,680
Let Wei Hao go!

422
00:25:05,039 --> 00:25:05,920
Wei Hao!

423
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:08,319
I beg you!

424
00:25:10,079 --> 00:25:11,400
I beg you!

425
00:25:11,599 --> 00:25:13,039
Let Wei Hao go!

426
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:42,960
Don't come over!

427
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:08,400
Brother Jie.

428
00:26:08,839 --> 00:26:09,640
What you asked me to investigate...

429
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,559
Zhou Ziheng did go to Duchen Temple yesterday,

430
00:26:12,039 --> 00:26:13,599
but he was attending a police-community event.

431
00:26:15,039 --> 00:26:16,720
Isn't that a bit too coincidental?

432
00:26:18,119 --> 00:26:19,119
I'll have someone watch him closely.

433
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:22,960
Investigate thoroughly from the past to now,

434
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:26,440
all interactions between Zhou Ziheng and Hao Yu.

435
00:26:28,240 --> 00:26:28,720
Understood.

436
00:26:44,519 --> 00:26:45,279
The master just left.

437
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:52,440
Why is your eye makeup smudged?

438
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:57,160
Maybe it was the incense smoke.

439
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:16,880
Stay away from Wei Hao and Zhong Jiali from now on.

440
00:27:17,480 --> 00:27:18,359
Don't go provoking them.

441
00:27:19,359 --> 00:27:21,279
What do you mean I'm provoking them?

442
00:27:22,359 --> 00:27:23,720
I'm the victim here.

443
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:25,079
I know that in your heart,

444
00:27:25,079 --> 00:27:26,480
you want to hack them to pieces.

445
00:27:27,160 --> 00:27:28,319
But they belong to Cang Feng.

446
00:27:28,720 --> 00:27:30,160
Only Uncle Kun can torture them.

447
00:27:30,359 --> 00:27:31,720
Anyone who goes against Cang Feng,

448
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:32,920
or betrays Uncle Kun,

449
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:35,279
will face consequences far worse than that.

450
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:40,039
So you taking me to see Wei Hao get beaten,

451
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:41,519
and Jiali making a fool of herself,

452
00:27:42,119 --> 00:27:43,720
wasn't to help me vent my anger.

453
00:27:44,599 --> 00:27:45,880
It was to threaten me.

454
00:27:48,039 --> 00:27:49,440
I have something else to ask you.

455
00:27:50,519 --> 00:27:51,599
That guy named Zhou...

456
00:27:51,599 --> 00:27:53,640
couldn't find evidence on Wei Hao for the longest time.

457
00:27:54,319 --> 00:27:55,400
As soon as he got injured and hospitalized,

458
00:27:55,599 --> 00:27:57,680
Wei Hao admitted to the crimes on the spot today.

459
00:27:58,759 --> 00:28:00,160
Isn't that a bit too coincidental?

460
00:28:05,240 --> 00:28:06,559
What are you implying?

461
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:11,039
I'm not implying anything.

462
00:28:12,799 --> 00:28:13,920
But remember this, Hao Yu.

463
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:17,720
As long as I, Ji Zhijie, am here,

464
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:18,680
in tomorrow's news,

465
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:21,000
not a single scandal from today will appear.

466
00:28:21,359 --> 00:28:23,000
You're not going to commit arson and murder again, are you?

467
00:28:24,119 --> 00:28:25,759
Isn't that the version of me you love?

468
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:30,920
Or is it the police?

469
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:37,680
You're hurting me.

470
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:53,920
You told me before,

471
00:28:53,920 --> 00:28:55,759
that piece of land your brother always wanted to buy for you,

472
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:58,240
was taken by Zhong Jiali by accident.

473
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:00,759
That place has always been a black market operation.

474
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:02,599
I've laundered it over these years.

475
00:29:05,119 --> 00:29:06,240
The nightclub is yours now.

476
00:29:08,119 --> 00:29:10,200
It's just that today's opening ceremony was a bit messy.

477
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:11,920
But I still have to congratulate you.

478
00:29:15,119 --> 00:29:15,799
Boss lady.

479
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:06,640
As long as I, Ji Zhijie, am here,

480
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:07,559
in tomorrow's news,

481
00:30:07,559 --> 00:30:09,920
not a single scandal from today will appear.

482
00:30:11,039 --> 00:30:11,920
Uncle Kun is looking for me.

483
00:30:12,519 --> 00:30:12,880
Okay, I got it.

484
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:13,720
I'll be there in ten minutes.

485
00:30:16,799 --> 00:30:17,559
I'll head out first.

486
00:30:28,519 --> 00:30:30,000
Mr. Ji, please look over here.

487
00:30:30,039 --> 00:30:30,559
Mr. Ji.

488
00:30:30,680 --> 00:30:31,680
Mr. Ji.

489
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:32,759
I know that in your heart,

490
00:30:32,759 --> 00:30:34,240
you want to hack them to pieces.

491
00:30:34,799 --> 00:30:35,960
But they belong to Cang Feng.

492
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:38,119
Only Uncle Kun can torture them.

493
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,480
Anyone who goes against Cang Feng,

494
00:30:39,599 --> 00:30:40,640
or betrays Uncle Kun,

495
00:30:41,279 --> 00:30:42,880
will face consequences far worse than that.

496
00:31:33,359 --> 00:31:33,880
Wei Hao.

497
00:31:36,119 --> 00:31:36,559
Wei Hao.

498
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:39,519
Wei Hao.

499
00:31:45,160 --> 00:31:45,759
Wei Hao.

500
00:31:48,519 --> 00:31:49,079
Bear with it a little.

501
00:31:53,559 --> 00:31:55,519
I should have killed Hao Yu sooner.

502
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:57,599
Then none of this would have happened.

503
00:31:58,160 --> 00:31:59,880
And now it caused you to lose the nightclub.

504
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:02,319
Don't move.

505
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:07,480
Wei Hao.

506
00:32:09,079 --> 00:32:10,480
The reason we keep losing,

507
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,559
is because we haven't caught any evidence,

508
00:32:14,279 --> 00:32:15,559
and we want her dead too badly.

509
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:18,079
She loves setting traps so much,

510
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:20,880
and is dead set on killing us.

511
00:32:23,279 --> 00:32:24,720
Then let's give her what she wants.

512
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,640
Someone stole the accounts from our black ledger.

513
00:32:35,279 --> 00:32:36,559
But you managed to get it back.

514
00:32:41,079 --> 00:32:41,799
A fake one.

515
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:47,960
Easy now.

516
00:32:54,880 --> 00:32:56,200
Find a way to get these words...

517
00:32:56,200 --> 00:32:57,640
to reach Hao Yu's ears.

518
00:32:58,599 --> 00:32:59,920
She's so anxious to kill you,

519
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:00,839
and to destroy Cang Feng.

520
00:33:01,119 --> 00:33:02,160
She will definitely try everything,

521
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:04,480
to find this fatal evidence through you,

522
00:33:05,559 --> 00:33:07,079
and hand it to her contact.

523
00:33:08,079 --> 00:33:09,079
When that time comes,

524
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:11,400
no matter if it's Zhou Ziheng, Wang Ziheng,

525
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:12,359
or Li Ziheng,

526
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:15,559
as long as we catch them making the exchange,

527
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:18,640
and catch them red-handed,

528
00:33:22,359 --> 00:33:24,599
you can clear your name with Uncle Kun.

529
00:33:25,799 --> 00:33:27,759
And we can take back everything we lost.

530
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:29,319
Do you understand?
